SauceBot! :D

SauceBot server:

  Build:
  $ coffee --compile --output server/bin/ server/src/

  Running:
  $ cd server/bin
  $ supervisor saucebot.js

  Dependencies:
    - CoffeeScript
    - Node.js
    + NPM
        - colors
        - socket.io
        - supervisor
        

SauceBot client:

  Build:
  $ coffee --compile --output client/bin/ client/src/

  Running:
  $ cd client/bin
  $ supervisor saucebot.js <channels> <username> <password>
    - <channels>: A list of JTV channels to join, separated by :
    - <username>: The bot's Justin.tv username
    - <password>: The bot's Justin.tv password
    
  Example:
  $ supervisor saucebot.js channel1:channel2:channel3 MyBot mahb0tpwd

  Dependencies:
    - CoffeeScript
    - Node.js
    + NPM
        - colors
        - socket.io
        - irc
        - supervisor
        
